CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: CNS Pharmaceuticals Inc is a preclinical stage pharmaceutical company focused on the development of anticancer drug candidates for the treatment of primary and metastatic brain and central nervous system tumors. It is involved in the development of Berubicin, which is a therapy for the treatment of glioblastoma.
